Protocol: KeyLookup

Types:
  Agent A, I, X;
  Number NKey;
  Public_key PKX;
  Function pk, sk;
  Token AuthTokA;

Knowledge:
  A: A, I, X, pk(I), AuthTokA;
  I: A, I, X, pk(I), sk(I), pk(X);

Actions:
  A -> I: A, X, AuthTokA, NKey
  I -> A: {| I, X, pk(X), NKey |}sk(I)

Goals:
  pk(X) secret between A,I
  A authenticates I on pk(X)